java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Dialog
      evaluations.EvaluationDialogue

public class EvaluationDialogue
extends org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Dialog

A Dialog box that allows the user to input data for an employee evaluation, and then returns that evaluation.
